OL,3,CHusband left 'devastated' after wife
OL,4,Ckilled by speeding driver
OL,6,FA man whose wife was killed by a
OL,7,Fspeeding driver outside their home has
OL,8,Fsaid her death has "destroyed" his
OL,9,Ffuture amid a rise in fatal road
OL,10,Ftraffic collisions.
OL,12,FLorraine Barrow, 57, was cycling home
OL,13,Ffrom work near Blackmore, in Somerset,
OL,14,Fwhen she was hit by a car travelling
OL,15,Fat 44mph on a road with a 30mph speed
OL,16,Flimit.
OL,18,FMrs Barrow died at the scene on 17
OL,19,FSeptember 2020, three days after her
OL,20,F35th wedding anniversary.
