OL,6,FFigures from Avon and Somerset police
OL,7,Fshow that since 2023, 121 road users
OL,8,Fin the force area have died in road
OL,9,Ftraffic collisions.
OL,11,FIt means that on average, one journey
OL,12,Fmade every week across Avon and
OL,13,FSomerset ends in tragic circumstances.
OL,15,FMrs Barrow's husband, Chris, said her
OL,16,Fdeath has "devastated" his family.
