OL,3,CHusband left 'devastated' after wife
OL,4,Ckilled by speeding driver
OL,6,F"I could see that it was obviously
OL,7,Fvery serious," he said. "All I could
OL,8,Fsee was blood flowing down into the
OL,9,Fdrain and no-one was really doing
OL,10,Fanything so I started CPR."
OL,12,FMr Barrow added: "I've lost not just
OL,13,Fmy wife, but my partner, my confidant,
OL,14,Fmy soul mate".
OL,16,FAvon and Somerset Police has
OL,17,Fcommissioned a film highlighting the
OL,18,Fimpact of fatal road traffic
OL,19,Fcollisions.
