OL,6,FThe one-minute video, which focuses on
OL,7,Fthe five most common causes of fatal
OL,8,Fcrashes, premiered to thousands of
OL,9,Ffootball fans at Ashton Gate, in
OL,10,FBristol, on Wednesday 12 February.
OL,12,FAccording to the force, drink and drug
OL,13,Fdriving, speeding, using a phone, not
OL,14,Fwearing a seat belt and careless
OL,15,Fdriving are the 'Fatal Five' reasons
OL,16,Ffor most collisions.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
