OL,4,Ckilled by speeding driver
OL,6,FHead of roads policing, Chief
OL,7,FInspector Robert Cheeseman, said: "We
OL,8,Fwant motorists to understand that poor
OL,9,Fdriving is the root cause of the
OL,10,Fmajority of collisions.
OL,12,F"These fatalities and injuries are
OL,13,Fpreventable. The choices we make
OL,14,Fbehind the wheel really do matter, and
OL,15,Fin making this film we hope to reach
OL,16,Fas many people as possible with this
OL,17,Fimportant message".
